Description: THE IDOLM@STER Break! Volume 3 (アイドルマスター ブレイク! 3, Aidorumasta Bureiku! 3) is a cover album released as a collaboration between the game The iDOLM@STER and the Bakemonogatari anime series. The mini-album is included in a limited manga of selected characters of The iDOLM@STER. It was released on June 2010.
